skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: cartoon crash alarm
Developer Terms of Use
des:
Forget those old, boring, buzz and jingle alarms! Get jolted out of bed each morning to the hilarious crash sounds from your favorite cartoons!

Cartoon Crash Alarm features 2 free crash alarms: "Airplane Problems," and "Failed Parachute," plus an especially gross get-out-of-bed snooze crash: "Goo Splash."

Get Cartoon Crash Gold to unlock seven MORE Cartoon Crash alarms including: "Ricochet," "Crash Wizard," "Free Fallin'," "Cratered," "Bungee Fail," "Rube Goldberg's Demise," and "Slingshot Disaster."

All crashes are 100% made from foley items, music instruments, and synthesizers. No coyotes, roadrunners, tomcats, or mice were harmed in their production.

FEEDBACK AND SUPPORT: If you enjoyed Cartoon Crash Alarm, please leave us a review telling us what you love, and what alarms you want to hear next! 

Icon courtesy of Freepik. Vector created by brgfx.
